{"title":"祖国，向克里姆宫倾听","authors":["牛汉"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":12,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，向克里姆宫倾听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走进克里姆宫的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想些什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向斯大林要说的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国底城市和乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢舞的行列"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在一队跟着一队的行进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站在雅罗斯拉夫车站的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联人民不息地呼喊着“乌拉！毛泽东！乌拉！毛泽东！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国又有多少个新解放的城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插起了红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你底人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你底战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也正在欢呼着你底名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们底手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全都向北极星伸出来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国底在地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正向莫斯科倾听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国底人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在向莫斯科倾听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样走进克里姆宫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎样和斯大林亲切的谈论着……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林底向东方伸出的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国底人民的熟悉的呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那手势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卅年来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直指引着我们奋勇前进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指给了我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的方向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国底大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，正在向克里姆宫倾听……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛听到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆宫底钟声在蓝色的莫斯科底天空回响着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和斯大林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正手挽着手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲热的谈论着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步地走过红场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁底墓顶上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们向着远方凝望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你们面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光彩地展开了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九，一二，二○。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}